  "lede": "AI (LLM) — <strong>ma'lumotlar bazasи emas</strong>, balki <strong>keyingи so'zни bashorat qiladigan</strong> model. Shuning uchun unга <strong>qanday murojaat qilsang — shunday javob olasan</strong>. Prompt — shu murojaat.",
  "doc": "<div class='prose'><h3>LLM qanday ishlaydi (sodda)</h3><p>Til modeli (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini) ulkan matnда o'qib, <strong>keyingи so'zни ehtimollик asosида bashorat qiladi</strong>. U \"bilmaydi\" — u <strong>davom ettiradi</strong>. Shuning uchun:</p><div class=\"chips\"><span class=\"chip t\">aniq so'rasang — aniq davom ettiradi</span><span class=\"chip t\">noaniq so'rasang — taxmin qiladi</span><span class=\"chip t\">kontekst bersang — moslashadi</span></div><h3>Garbage in → garbage out</h3><p>Yomon prompt = yomon javob. Modelни ayblamadan oldin <strong>promptни yaxshila</strong>. Natijaning 80% promptга bog'liq.</p><div class=\"exlist\"><div class=\"ex\"><b>Tell me about dogs.</b><span>juda keng — model nimani aytishni bilmaydi</span></div><div class=\"ex\"><b>Explain 3 key facts about caring for a puppy, for a first-time owner, in simple terms.</b><span>aniq — yaxshi javob</span></div></div><h3>Hallucination (to'qib chiqarish)</h3><p>AI ba'zан <strong>ishonчли ohangда noto'g'ri ma'lumot</strong> beradi. Bu — galyutsinatsiya. Shuning uchun muhim faktларни <strong>doim tekshir</strong>.</p><div class=\"callout\"><span class=\"ic\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"8\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"12\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"16\" x2=\"12.01\" y2=\"16\"/></svg></span><div><p>Asosiy fikr</p><p>Sen — <strong>rejissyorsan</strong>. Model qobiliyatli aktyor, lekin u sening niyatингни o'qiy olmaydi. Qancha aniq yo'naltirsang, shuncha yaxshi natija.</p></div></div></div>",
