  "doc": "<div class='prose'><h3>Zero / One / Few-shot</h3><div class=\"exlist\"><div class=\"ex\"><b>Zero-shot</b><span>misolсиз, faqat vazifa</span></div><div class=\"ex\"><b>One-shot</b><span>bitta misol bilan</span></div><div class=\"ex\"><b>Few-shot</b><span>bir necha misol bilan — naqsh aniq</span></div></div><h3>Few-shot misol</h3><p>Modelга \"kirish → chiqish\" namunаларини ber, keyin yangiсини so'ra. U formatни va uslubни nusxa qiladi.</p><h3>Chain-of-thought (bosqичма-bosqич)</h3><p>Mantiqий yoki matematик vazifада <strong>\"Think step by step\"</strong> desang, model oraliq qadamларни ko'rsatadi va kamroq xato qiladi.</p><div class=\"exlist\"><div class=\"ex\"><b>Solve this. Think step by step, then give the final answer.</b><span>qadamlar + yakuniy javob</span></div></div><h3>Delimiter (ajratgich)</h3><p>Matn va ko'rsatma aralashmasин uchun ajratgich ishlat: <code class='inline'>\"\"\"</code>, <code class='inline'>###</code>, yoki teglar.</p><div class=\"callout\"><span class=\"ic\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"8\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"12\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"16\" x2=\"12.01\" y2=\"16\"/></svg></span><div><p>Maslahat</p><p>Few-shot — eng kuchli texnikаlardan. Modelга \"shунинг kabi qil\" deб <strong>2-3 sifatли misol</strong> bersang, natija keskin yaxshilanadi.</p></div></div></div>",
